OL,3,CNurses taking trust to tribunal over
OL,4,Ctrans colleague's use of changing rooms
OL,6,FTribunal Judge Stuart Robinson said:
OL,7,F"These are important proceedings. The
OL,8,Fissues are complex."
OL,10,FThe trust claimed a postponement was
OL,11,Fnecessary to allow more time for an
OL,12,Finternal investigation to be completed.
OL,14,FJudge Robinson said the hearings will
OL,15,Ftake four weeks, not the original
OL,16,Festimate of three, given around 30
OL,17,Fwitnesses are expected to give
OL,18,Fevidence.
OL,20,FHe scheduled the case to be heard from
OL,21,F20 October.
