OL,3,CNurses taking trust to tribunal over
OL,4,Ctrans colleague's use of changing rooms
OL,6,FAhead of the hearing, nurse Bethany
OL,7,FHutchison, speaking on behalf of the
OL,8,Fgroup, set out their view.
OL,10,F"We are nurses who love our jobs and
OL,11,Four patients and only want to be
OL,12,Fafforded the dignity of getting
OL,13,Fdressed and undressed for work without
OL,14,Fa man present," she said.
OL,16,F"I would like to remind everyone that
OL,17,Fwe are doing this for the safety and
OL,18,Fdignity of every woman and girl across
OL,19,Fsociety."
