OL,3,CNurses taking trust to tribunal over
OL,4,Ctrans colleague's use of changing rooms
OL,6,FThe nurses are being supported by the
OL,7,FChristian Legal Centre.
OL,9,FA spokesperson for the trust said:
OL,10,F"County Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust is fully committed to
OL,12,Fsupporting all members of our staff
OL,13,Fand ensuring a safe, respectful and
OL,14,Finclusive working environment.
OL,16,F"We recognise that legal proceedings
OL,17,Fare currently underway and we are
OL,18,Fengaging with the process in full
OL,19,Faccordance with employment law and the
OL,20,Ftribunal's instructions.
